about.summary: Find and fix problems in your JavaScript code.

name: eslint
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "eslint" %}
{% set version = "8.43.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/archive/refs/tags/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1c3f3f4eeb4ad99c254475402d855de2bf2977ca9919eb666662e4da733d435b

build:
  number: 0

requirements:
  build:
    - nodejs
  host:
    - nodejs
    - yarn <2
  run:
    - nodejs

test:
  commands:
    - eslint --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/eslint/eslint
  license: MIT
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - ThirdPartyLicenses.txt
  summary: Find and fix problems in your JavaScript code.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy

about.summary: Find and fix problems in your JavaScript code.
